<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>最近一周 GitHub 技术速递</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #000000;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(107, 72, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #001233 0%, #0a0a0a 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(0, 18, 51, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            min-height: 100vh;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #00F0FF;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.5);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        h1::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.8), transparent);
            animation: glow 3s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes glow {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
            50% { opacity: 1; }
        }
        
        .generated-info {
            text-align: center;
            color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.7);
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 25px;
            background: rgba(0, 18, 51, 0.85);
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: #00F0FF;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.4);
        }
        
        article {
            background: rgba(0, 18, 51, 0.7);
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        article::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.8), transparent);
            opacity: 0.8;
            animation: glow 3s infinite;
        }
        
        article:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            border-color: #00F0FF;
        }
        
        h3 {
            color: #00F0FF;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        h3 a {
            color: #00F0FF;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        h3 a:hover {
            color: #6B48FF;
            text-decoration: underline;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(107, 72, 255, 0.5);
        }
        
        .summary {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        ul {
            margin-left: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .recommendation {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #00F0FF;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        .detail {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            line-height: 1.8;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .meta {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.7);
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        .topics {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .topic {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.15);
            color: #00F0FF;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .topic:hover {
            background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.25);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>最近一周 GitHub 技术速递</h1>
        <div class="generated-info">
            生成时间：{{generatedAt}} | 涵盖领域：{{domainsText}}
        </div>
        
        {{{content}}}
    </div>
</body>
</html>